{{version031}}
{{Flavour|Heals a small amount of damage to the caster's body.}}

'''Minor Healing''' is a monster-only spell which restores the caster's health; the amount is determined by the caster's [[hit dice]]. Note that monsters can cast this spell when they are outside the player's [[line of sight]].

